com.innowhere.jnieasy.core.data
Interface NativeArrayOfArray

All Superinterfaces:
CanBeNativeCapable, CanBeNativeCapableArray, NativeArray, NativeCapable, NativeFieldContainer, NativeObjectArray, NativeObjectFieldContainer, NativeSingleFieldContainer
public interface NativeArrayOfArray
extends CanBeNativeCapableArray

The NativeArrayOfArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes wrapping multidimensional native arrays.

A multidimensional Java array is wrapped with a predefined internal class implementing this interface, unless a user defined multidimensional array is used. User defined multidimensional arrays implements this interface too.

Author:
Jose M. Arranz Santamaria
